channel.title: Is it me or
channel.description:
Is everyone moving onto the 400 series servers :|
It seems that everywhere i look i see either hyperion upgraded to 400+, a 400+ framework being worked on, some sort of old skewl remake or some shitty delta server.
Where *WHERE* is the originality?
Come on guys!

item.title: Is it me or
item.dc:creator: @cows1471 cows1471
item.description:
@cows1471 wrote:

Explisionist:

I use 317s no matter what. Mainly because they are beautiful… All the good bases are 317, and they are the most known when it comes to coding… You can make a 317 with HD, etc… Make it look like a 508+ and it will still be better… Make the 508 use the 317 cache and the original 317 will still own it… No matter what you do a 317 will be the best.

Do you not mean texture / model replacement not “HD”
